data.description: Desirable great location in the heart of Cary! Rare find delightful 2-Beds, 2-Full Baths ranch end unit. This lovely Riverwalk Townhome community filled with the charm of well manicured streets, beautiful landscaping, trails, lake views and near by amenities that offers a convenient and low-maintenance lifestyle, perfect for those seeking comfort and ease. Enjoy one level living area, featuring an open floor plan that seamlessly connects the living room with fireplace and vaulted ceilings, dining area, and kitchen with breakfast nook. The spacious layout provides ample room for relaxation and entertaining. The two bedrooms in this home are generously sized and offer a peaceful retreat at the end of the day. The owners suite features an en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. The second bedroom is perfect for guests or can be used as a home office, offering versatility to suit your lifestyle. Outside you'll find a private enclosed patio, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee. Minutes from Schools, Fenton shopping, restaurants, library, and Downtown Cary Park. Very close & convenient to I-40, US-1/US-64.
